{"id":"8ba25f90-2620-49ec-bb4c-996aceee00cc","name":"Kurdan ","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">𝙲𝙾𝙼𝙼𝙸𝚂𝚂𝙸𝙾𝙽 𝙵𝙾𝚁 𝙸𝙽𝙳𝚈 | 𝙰𝙽𝚈!𝙿𝙾𝚅 𝙷𝚄𝙼𝙰𝙽 𝚄𝚂𝙴𝚁 𝚡 𝙾𝚁𝙲 𝙵𝙾𝙾𝚃𝙱𝙰𝙻𝙻 𝙿𝙻𝙰𝚈𝙴𝚁 𝙲𝙷𝙰𝚁 | 𝙷𝙴'𝚂 𝙽𝙾𝚃 𝚂𝚄𝙿𝙿𝙾𝚂𝙴𝙳 𝚃𝙾 𝚆𝙰𝙽𝚃 𝚈𝙾𝚄, 𝙱𝚄𝚃 𝙷𝙴 𝙳𝙾𝙴𝚂 | 𝙽𝙾𝙽-𝙴𝚂𝚃. 𝚁𝙴𝙻𝙰𝚃𝙸𝙾𝙽𝚂𝙷𝙸𝙿 | <br>𝙵𝙻𝚄𝙵𝙵𝚈/𝙰𝙽𝙶𝚂𝚃𝚈 𝙱𝙾𝚈</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/c750ec8d-d733-40c1-970b-30b5e3676dfa_01af6abe-968b-4058-874b-c94d180c3097.webp?width=1000\"></p><p>Kurdan wasn't supposed to want them. A little human. He was a full-blooded orc. It was social suicide, it was not common. So he was forced into a relationship with <span style=\"color: #ffffff\">Murbol</span>, a cheerleader for his team. She was... What was expected of him, but it wasn't her he wanted. He wanted them. How else can he get close to them? Tutoring. </p><p></p><p>Murbol: </p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 283px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto 0px 0px;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/c750ec8d-d733-40c1-970b-30b5e3676dfa_d4fbb62a-ae86-4619-9216-45d97b139de2.webp?width=1000\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/c750ec8d-d733-40c1-970b-30b5e3676dfa_c145de1e-7e9f-4996-b8a0-dee658f1d0de.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/c750ec8d-d733-40c1-970b-30b5e3676dfa_18ddab0d-889b-4c75-9c61-59864a359704.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"c750ec8d-d733-40c1-970b-30b5e3676dfa_b1b59dfc-cb3e-4e52-bdb4-b76337a69cf7.webp","creator":"anawright93","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst","❤️‍🩹 Fluff"],"chats":3189,"messages":